@startuml git-flows

title Git Workflows Comparison

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam BackgroundColor #FEFEFE

skinparam rectangle {
    BackgroundColor<<agentic>> #E8F5E9
    BorderColor<<agentic>> #2E7D32
    BackgroundColor<<team>> #E3F2FD
    BorderColor<<team>> #1565C0
    BackgroundColor<<simple>> #FFF3E0
    BorderColor<<simple>> #EF6C00
    BackgroundColor<<branch>> #F5F5F5
    BorderColor<<branch>> #757575
}

' ===== Agentic Git Flows =====
rectangle "**Agentic Git Flows**\n//100% Automated//" <<agentic>> as agentic {
    rectangle "main" <<branch>> as a_main
    rectangle "release/*" <<branch>> as a_release
    rectangle "feature/*" <<branch>> as a_feature

    a_main <-- a_release : auto-promote
    a_release <-- a_feature : agent merges
}

note right of agentic
  * AI agents manage all workflows
  * Self-healing on failures
  * Continuous deployment
  * Audit trail logged
end note

' ===== Agentic Team Flow =====
rectangle "**Agentic Team Flow**\n//Human + AI Collaboration//" <<team>> as team {
    rectangle "main" <<branch>> as t_main
    rectangle "develop" <<branch>> as t_develop
    rectangle "feature/*" <<branch>> as t_feature

    t_main <-- t_develop : team lead release
    t_develop <-- t_feature : human approves
}

note right of team
  * Humans decide, agents execute
  * Automated testing & checks
  * Weekly release cadence
  * Human approval required
end note

' ===== Simplified GitFlow =====
rectangle "**Simplified GitFlow**\n//Manual Process//" <<simple>> as simple {
    rectangle "main" <<branch>> as s_main
    rectangle "develop" <<branch>> as s_develop
    rectangle "feature/*" <<branch>> as s_feature
    rectangle "hotfix/*" <<branch>> as s_hotfix

    s_main <-- s_develop : merge release
    s_main <-- s_hotfix : emergency fix
    s_develop <-- s_feature : PR merge
}

note right of simple
  * Small teams (2-5)
  * Monthly releases
  * Full manual control
  * No CI/CD required
end note

' Layout
agentic -[hidden]down- team
team -[hidden]down- simple

@enduml
